Mantra Venture Group Ltd.


            
            Mantra Venture Group Ltd. develops and commercializes alternative energy technologies and services. It acquired and owned technologies like MRFC (Mixed-Reactant Fuel Cell) design is a revolutionary fuel cell concept and ERC (Electro-Reduction) is a process for the electro-reduction of carbon dioxide from industrial sources. The company operates as a clean technology development company through its subsidiary Mantra Energy Alternatives Ltd. Mantra Venture Group was founded by Larry Kristof on January 22, 2007 and is headquartered in Surrey, Canada.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


